decks.notes: The main focus of this Legacy Aggro - Burn deck is to rapidly deal damage to the opponent through quick and efficient spells and creatures. By using cards like Eidolon of the Great Revel, Monastery Swiftspear, and Goblin Guide to pressure the opponent, alongside powerful burn spells such as Lightning Bolt, Lava Spike, and Price of Progress, this deck aims to win the game before the opponent can stabilize. Additionally, cards like Fireblast and Roiling Vortex provide additional burst damage and disruption to maintain the aggressive tempo.

This deck focuses on quickly deploying evasive creatures like Ornithopter and Baleful Strix, while using Ninjas like Yuriko and Ingenious Infiltrator to deal damage and draw cards. It also includes disruption cards like Stifle and Force of Will to control the opponent's spells, while Retrofitter Foundry provides a way to generate additional creatures. The deck aims to apply pressure early in the game and maintain card advantage through the use of its creature abilities and card draw spells.
